name: sak-maestro
title: Emcee: Sak Maestro | FlipTop Battle League
description: Sak Maestro may have lost his debut battle against Zero Hour at the inaugural Pakusganay event, but it was the night where people witnessed his one-of-a-kind technical skill. Battle rap fans praised his intricate multis and wordplays as well as his calm but deadly delivery. He continued to showcase his advanced style in his next matches, collecting a few dominant victories along the way.
